claim.claim-text:
An electronic device (100) comprising:
- a memory (160);
- a display unit (151);
- a communication unit (110) configured to communicate with one or more external electronic devices (10); and
- a controller (180) configured to;
- share screens with the external electronic devices (10) through the communication unit (110),
- capture a screen displayed on the display unit (151) when a screen capture signal instructing the screen displayed on the display unit (151) to be captured is received, and
- store the captured image at least one of in the memory (160) and in at least one of the external electronic devices.
